  <brief_title>Amitriptyline and Paroxetine Treatment of Major Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>Hypothalamus-pituitary-adrenal System: Role of the Mineralocorticoid Receptor and Longitudinal Study in Depressed Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
